{{Top|leg}}
The [[Travis Motors]] '''Starlifter''' was a cargo loader used by [[Alfex Cargo Stacks]] on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

Piloted by a [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] in its one-seat cockpit or a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] in a special socket, the Starlifter carried cargo with four landing claws that emerged from the corners of its flat bottom.<ref name="CCW" />

Alfex, as a front for [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]], made its own special modification to the Starlifter, hiding a pair of [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] in each vehicle.<ref name="CCW" />

